 (Чингис хааны хаяал), Бүри бөх нь Хабул хааны дөрөв дахь хүү Хутугту Монхорын хүү байжээ.\\n\\nИдэр нас\\n\"}","env":{},"headers":{"Accept":"application/json, text/plain, */*","Content-Type":"application/json"},"maxBodyLength":-1,"maxContentLength":-1,"method":"post","timeout":0,"transformRequest":[null],"transformResponse":[null],"transitional":{"clarifyTimeoutError":false,"forcedJSONParsing":true,"silentJSONParsing":true},"url":"/api/generate","xsrfCookieName":"XSRF-TOKEN","xsrfHeaderName":"X-XSRF-TOKEN"},"message":"Request failed with status code 403","name":"AxiosError","stack":"AxiosError: Request failed with status code 403\n    at settle (http://localhost:3001/_next/static/chunks/node_modules_af0f0175._.js:3479:16)\n    at XMLHttpRequest.onloadend (http://localhost:3001/_next/static/chunks/node_modules_af0f0175._.js:3994:174)\n    at Axios.request (http://localhost:3001/_next/static/chunks/node_modules_af0f0175._.js:4798:49)\n    at async handleGenerate (http://localhost:3001/_next/static/chunks/src_51b02eb9._.js:988:33)","status":403}
